#include<stdio.h>
#include<string.h>

main()
{
    int i,t,day,year,res_day;
    char month[10],str[90];

    scanf("%d",&t);

    for(i=0;i<t;i++){
        scanf("%s",str);
        day=(str[0]-48)*10+(str[1]-48);
        month[0]=str[3];
        month[1]=str[4];
        month[2]=str[5];
        month[3]='\0';
        year = (str[7]-48)*1000+(str[8]-48)*100+(str[9]-48)*10+(str[10]-48);
        if(strcmp(month,"JAN")==0){
            res_day=day;
        }else if(strcmp(month,"FEB")==0){
            res_day=day+31;
        }else if(strcmp(month,"MAR")==0){
            res_day=day+59;
        }else if(strcmp(month,"APR")==0){
            res_day=day+90;
        }else if(strcmp(month,"MAY")==0){
            res_day=day+120;
        }else if(strcmp(month,"JUN")==0){
            res_day=day+151;
        }else if(strcmp(month,"JUL")==0){
            res_day=day+181;
        }else if(strcmp(month,"AUG")==0){
            res_day=day+212;
        }else if(strcmp(month,"SEP")==0){
            res_day=day+243;
        }else if(strcmp(month,"OCT")==0){
            if(day<=27)
                res_day=day+273;
        }

        if(strcmp(month,"JAN")==0 ){
            printf("Case %d: %d Hundreds\n",i+1,day);
        }else if(strcmp(month,"FEB")==0){
            printf("Case %d: %d Hundreds\n",i+1,day+31);
        }else if((year%100!=0 && year%4==0)||year%400==0){

            res_day++;
            if(strcmp(month,"DEC")==0 && day<=25){
                printf("Case %d: %d Tens\n",i+1,day+35);
            }else if(strcmp(month,"NOV")==0){
                 printf("Case %d: %d Tens\n",i+1,day+5);
            }else if(strcmp(month,"OCT")==0 && day>26){
                 printf("Case %d: %d Tens\n",i+1,day-26);
            }else if(day>=26 && strcmp(month,"DEC")==0){
                printf("Case %d: %d Ones\n",i+1,day-25);
            }else {
                printf("Case %d: %d Hundreds\n",i+1,res_day);
            }

        }else {
            if(strcmp(month,"DEC")==0 && day<=26){
                printf("Case %d: %d Tens\n",i+1,day+34);

            }else if(strcmp(month,"NOV")==0){
                 printf("Case %d: %d Tens\n",i+1,day+4);

            }else if(strcmp(month,"OCT")==0 && day>27){
                 printf("Case %d: %d Tens\n",i+1,day-27);

            }else if(day>=27 && strcmp(month,"DEC")==0){
                printf("Case %d: %d Ones\n",i+1,day-26);
                }else {
                printf("Case %d: %d Hundreds\n",i+1,res_day);
            }
        }


    }
}
